@startuml pipeline-activity
!theme plain
title 파이프라인 단계 (collect → analyze → summarize → dedup → letter_generate)

skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F0F8FF
skinparam activityBorderColor #333
skinparam defaultFontName SansSerif

start

:collect;
note right
  sources.yaml 로드
  RSS / hnrss / reddit_rss / crawl
  병렬 수집 → 기준일(date) 필터
  checkpoint: collect.json
end note

:analyze;
note right
  collect 항목을 청크(80개) 단위로
  ThreadPoolExecutor(4) 병렬
  skills/analyze.md + LLM
  checkpoint: analyze.json
end note

:summarize;
note right
  analyze 결과 전체를
  skills/summarize.md + LLM
  checkpoint: summarize.json
end note

:dedup;
note right
  최근 7일 index 항목과
  Jaccard 유사도 + LLM 판정
  threshold 0.5
  checkpoint: dedup.json
end note

:letter_generate;
note right
  skills/letter_generate.md + LLM
  data/letters/YYYY-MM-DD.md
  data/index/YYYY-MM-DD.json
  checkpoint: letter_generate.json
end note

stop

@enduml
